com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.card
Class ListCard

java.lang.Object
  com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.card.ListCard
All Implemented Interfaces:
Parcelable
public class ListCard
extends Object
implements Parcelable

A specialised type of List for maintaining a list of Cards in a DeckOfCards.

A list may contain no more than MAX_CARDS cards. Each card added to the list must have a unique id.

Author:
mcaunter
See Also:
DeckOfCards
